TO AN APPLICANT IS TO SEE IF THE MONTHLY MORTGAGE PAYMENT
WOULD BE MORE THAN A CERTAIN FIXED PER CENT OF THAT
APPLICANT'S GROSS MONTHLY INCOME. IN THIS PROGRAM THE
MORTGAGE INTEREST RATE AND TERM IS KNOWN, ALONG WITH THE
